ry returns with message of unity|publisher=[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]]|date=July 15, 2016|accessdate=July 16, 2016|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130163857/https://sports.yahoo.com/news/katy-perry-returns-message-unity-071003933--oly.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[大西洋（杂志）|大西洋]]》作家索菲·吉爾伯特写这首歌是：「一个关于决心的无力主题曲，用了一些回声机器和用一些具有侵略性的隐喻，去引起像[[凱妮絲·艾佛汀（虚构人物）|凱妮絲·艾佛汀]]，[[马娅·安杰卢|马娅·安杰卢]]和[[耶稣|耶稣]]类似各种各样的偶像。」<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Gilbert|first1=Sophie|title=Katy vs. Britney: Can Either Redeem Pop in 2016?|url=http://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2016/07/katy-vs-britney-who-can-save-pop-music-in-2016/491531/|journal=The Atlantic|accessdate=July 16, 2016|date=July 15, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108101549/https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2016/07/katy-vs-britney-who-can-save-pop-music-in-2016/491531/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的贝尼·拉特利夫称它为一首「缓步的」歌曲<ref name="TNYT1">{{cite news|author1=Pareles, Jon|author2=Ratliff, Ben|author3=Caramica, Jon|title=The Playlist: Katy Perry's Limp Olympics Anthem and Justice's Grooving Return|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/16/arts/music/playlist-katy-perry-rise-justice.html|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=July 16, 2016|date=July 15, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108110601/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/16/arts/music/playlist-katy-perry-rise-justice.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的一则评论中，凯文·唐奈称这首歌是「开始是徘徊气氛和小调的频率合成，直到一首强大的副歌迸发了。」<ref name="Rise - EW"/>

这首歌共长3分23秒钟<ref name=iTunes>{{cite web|title=Rise – Single by Katy Perry|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/rise/id1134580086|publisher=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]|date=July 15, 2016|accessdate=August 29, 2016|archive-date=2016-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160922174346/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/rise/id1134580086|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它用了[[降E小调|降E小调]]和以每一分钟110.5的[[速度_(音樂)|拍子]]的[[拍号|同一时间]]节奏，凯蒂在这首歌的声音跨度是从C♯4到E♭5<ref name="sheet">{{cite web|title=Katy Perry 'Rise' Sheet Music in Eb Minor|url=http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0165173|publisher=Musicnotes.com|accessdate=July 20, 2016|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929183349/https://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0165173|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
